item.title: Plz help me someone just gemme suggestion :(
item.dc:creator: @Siccc Siccc
item.description:
@Siccc wrote:

Alright if you got the models. Don’t extract them leave them in the .rar format. Now place them into the models folder into your client. Then get the ints. Place them in class8.java file in your client. Compile. Go to your server go to items.cfg add the item there and its stats. Then go on your server and type this in “add model (model number)” With out the “” and do it for both models. The model number is the name of the .rar file. So after that you should have your item and model! Congrats.
